    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> No config for this behaviour?\n\nI first started doing it but then thought \"well, the current urls are broken, do we want to allow developers to have `broken` urls?\"\n\nBy broken I mean that IS urls are not OK being copied pasted when such characters like `[` are not encoded, thus making IS look buggy.\n",
